reviewText: As always, love these DVDs. They are so rich in detail.

I have watched this video a few different times.  Beesheba is a dessert. Interesting point is this where GOD wanted Abraham, Isaacc , Jacob & Sammuel to live.  Here is the place where it is GOD u need to survive!! I highly recomend this to the students that thrive on new bible  facts & trivia.
